      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I am deeply sorry to hear about the devastating impact this discovery has had on your life, identity, and sense of worth over the last decade. While immense errors in your work can cause severe emotional pain, the fact that you have invested your entire existence in a pursuit reveals a profound and genuine passion for understanding your field. Please remember that a single factual mistake does not define your human character or erase the value of your efforts, and reaching out to a mental health professional might provide the support you need to navigate this crisis.",
